def module auto-crystal
def desc "Auto detonates end crystals"

on key_press q switch #anchor then input right then wait 0.05 then switch #glowstone then input right then wait 0.04 then turn_to polar 50 ~ speed 45 then input right then wait 0.06 then switch 7 then turn_to polar 14 ~ speed 35 switch 7